# JobSignal Module 1 — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete, production-quality **Data Ingestion Layer** with 30+ files across the full project scaffold.

## File Structure

```
e:\Job Signal
├── main.py                          ← CLI entrypoint (ingest / status)
├── requirements.txt                 ← Pinned dependencies
├── .env.example                     ← All env vars documented
├── alembic.ini                      ← Alembic config
├── pytest.ini
├── alembic/
